		<div class="lia-message-body-content">
			
                
                    <BLOCKQUOTE><TABLE border="1"><TBODY><TR><TD><BLOCKQUOTE><TABLE border="1"><TBODY><TR><TD>I decided to write a chapter today, as I don't want to have to on the Nexus Tower release date. Enjoy!<BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />Chapter 20 &gt;&gt;&gt;<BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />I wake up to see Numb Chuck's face staring at me. <BR /><BR />"Ane you ok?" he asks.<BR /><BR />"I... couldn't be better," I say. And, it's the truth. I feel fine.<BR /><BR />"Well, then, get up, and come on!"<BR /><BR />I get up, and follow him out the door of the room I'm in.<BR /><BR />"So, what was I hit by?" I ask him.<BR /><BR />"You were hit by shuriken, thrown by a Ninja," he answers. We walk in scilence until we reach a room. Some others are already there, and others are showing up. Surprisingly, no one is injured. There's about two dozen of us here, along with Numb Chuck, Zip Lash, and Kenjin the Wise.<BR /><BR />The room is carpeted, with steps that we sit on on one end, and a white board at the other. After everyone's filed in, Numb Chuck stands in front of us, and says, "Alright. you all survived some combat. But, many of you were injured in it, and if not for us three here," he gestures at Zip Lash and Kenjin, "The battle would have gone a completely different way. So, we need to train you guys in how to use weapons."<BR /><BR />He starts pacing, and then continues, "How well you pay attention in the next few days will determine your entire future."<BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />Numb Chuck hands out swords to all of us. "So, I suppose you're all wondering why we learn to use swords at all, or any other melee weapons. We've got guns, so why use them at all," he says. We all nod our heads.<BR /><BR />"Well then..." he says, and goes on to explain.<BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />The reason is cost and rarity. Because of the body armor worn by everone, made of a minerla called Obsidan, which is both light and strong. The only material that can cut through it is Plutonium, which is extremely rare and costly. So, a few ways were found to get around this.<BR /><BR />One was to use melee weapons, as you get infinite uses out of it.<BR /><BR />Another was to use arrows, as you can pick them up, and use them again after firing them.<BR /><BR />A third was to use guns, just limitedly, and use some other weapon. Numb Chuck explains that even Hael Storm's pistol has onyl six shots in it at any one time. And he's probally the richest man in the Universe!<BR /><BR />The final method was to use a technique used by the Space Muarader's blaster. It can go through Obsidan, but, to get through, it requires the blast be very, very weak. So, it does little damage. <BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />Numb Chuck finishes explaining, and it finally makes sense, why they use melee weapons here. Then, we start training. </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />Cool! I was right about the shuriken! <img class="emoticon emoticon-smile" id="smile" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/smile.png" alt="Smile" title="Smile" /> Unless you just added it after I guessed <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />Nice explanation of the obsidian armor <img class="emoticon emoticon-happy" id="happy" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/happy.png" alt="Happy" title="Happy" /> Good chapter overall, other then thee typoso.' <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />--Hurricane, Xtreme Daredevil<BR /> </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />I actually just added it because you guessed that. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /> And, I wanted to explain why we do use close range weapons, instead of guns, in LU.<BR /><BR />-Formic<BR />-Milligan in game
                
            
			
				
			
			
