		<div class="lia-message-body lia-component-body" id="messagebodydisplay_0_5" class="lia-message-body">
	
		<div class="lia-message-body-content">
			
                
                    Author's Note &gt;&gt;&gt;<BR /><BR />So, I have finished the first "Book" in the Nightfall Incident Series. each "Book" will have a title. The one I have just finished is called "The Nightfall Incident".<BR />To better tell the story I will be switching over to thrid person, past tense for the next "Book". <BR />I am not sure how many "Books" I will write. All I can say is, they will all be longer than this on.<BR />I will continue to write on this topic. This is where all future parts of the books will go. I will not create a new one.<BR />I shoud start writing the next "Book" a few days after Nexus Tower comes out. Though, I hope this topic still remains active!<BR />I must now thank everyone who has even opened up this topic, and especially those who have comented often on this topic. Without you guys, the story wouldn't still be going on.<BR /><BR />I had come up with the idea for a story like this about a month before I started writing. It was origionally going to take place on Earth, with only the plsyers of LU able to stop the Maelstrom.<BR />When I started writing, I only had a vague idea for the end of the entire series, a few chapters ahead, but nothing in the middle. I must admit, now, I still don't have tons planned! But, I've got the basic plot. And, I've writen the next few chapters in my head.<BR />I hope everyone enjoy the next "Book"!<BR /><BR />-Formic<BR />-Milligan in game
                
            
			
				
			
			
				<div>
	
</div>
			
			
            
            
            
            
		</div>
		
		
	
</div>

		
		
		
		
	
	
					
			
		
			
				
		
	
			
		
			
				
		
	
			
		
			
				
